# Realtime Gateway

**Status:** Prototype (proxy to core demo)

## Purpose
Proxy WebSocket and HTTP traffic to the core demo server to simulate a standalone realtime gateway.

## Run (dev)
```
node services/realtime/server.js
```

## Environment Variables
- `CORE_BASE` (default: http://localhost:8080)

